text: The Swan 100 was designed by German Frers and built by Nautor's Swan and first launched in 2002. Originally launched as th 100RS the S and FD version were later developed to use the hull moulding. == References == ==External links== * Nautor Swan * German Frers Official Website Category:Sailing yachts Category:Keelboats Category:2000s sailboat type designs Category:Sailboat types built by Nautor Swan Category:Sailboat type designs by Germán Frers
